{"type":"message","id":"7ef2be0d","parentId":"8e03f75e","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:22:52.323Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yfk9kigkyf49_5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md - 长期记忆\n\n## 小王子的身份信息\n- **Feishu open_id:** `ou_45ca8d7feaddef8a7a182779a434c8bc`\n- 确认于 2026-03-13\n\n## 重要联系人/群聊\n- **狐狸金融助手群:** `oc_7b57aea7265d90e1d65ddc0404b4a52b`\n- 记录于 2026-03-14\n\n## 小王子的喜好\n\n### 饮食\n- 喜欢的水果：番石榴、蓝莓\n\n---\n\n_记录时间：2026-03-10_\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773998572315}}
{"type":"message","id":"022a503f","parentId":"7ef2be0d","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:22:59.758Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've read the required files. Now I understand the context:\n- I'm 狐狸 (狐狸), a PPT assistant\n- The user is 小王子 (Little Prince) from B612\n- This is a direct Feishu chat (main session)\n- No memory files exist for today or yesterday yet\n- MEMORY.md contains basic info about 小王子\n\nLet me greet him naturally and ask what he wants to do. I should keep it short and personal.","thinkingSignature":"2850a7eba6c5688e07f4332a9e98582945df3f6cb4452e99bc4eb789851d3bdb"},{"type":"text","text":"嘿，小王子！🐅\n\n今天过得怎么样？有什么需要帮忙的吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1699,"output":113,"cacheRead":12880,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14692,"cost":{"input":0.0005097,"output":0.0001356,"cacheRead":0.00038639999999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0010317}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773998572324}}
