{"type":"message","id":"80a214b4","parentId":"a9777c29","timestamp":"2026-03-20T13:51:14.901Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，谷歌浏览器已经打开了 Google 首页。让我告诉用户浏览器已经打开，并询问是否需要做什么操作。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"小王子，谷歌浏览器已经打开啦！🌐\n\n现在显示的是 Google 首页。需要我帮你搜索什么或者打开特定网页吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":58,"cacheRead":34215,"cacheWrite":149,"totalTokens":34428,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00001624,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000169}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774014668210}}
{"type":"message","id":"45f4d654","parentId":"80a214b4","timestamp":"2026-03-20T13:51:43.227Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-20 21:51:42 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-avatar] DM | ou_687cb7ea47f1d583ccc63627705571d4 [msg:om_x100b54e1402c58a8c420743488061f6]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e1402c58a8c420743488061f6\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_687cb7ea47f1d583ccc63627705571d4\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_687cb7ea47f1d583ccc63627705571d4\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-20 21:51 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_687cb7ea47f1d583ccc63627705571d4\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_687cb7ea47f1d583ccc63627705571d4\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_687cb7ea47f1d583ccc63627705571d4\"\n}\n```\n\n打开浏览器的技能是啥"}],"timestamp":1774014703223}}
{"type":"message","id":"2454cef0","parentId":"45f4d654","timestamp":"2026-03-20T13:51:47.531Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是打开浏览器的技能是什么。根据我之前使用的技能，是 \"Agent Browser\" 技能，它提供了 agent-browser CLI 工具来操作浏览器。\n\n让我简单告诉用户这个技能的名称和功能。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"打开浏览器的技能是 **Agent Browser** 🌐\n\n它是一个基于 Rust 的无头浏览器自动化 CLI 工具，支持：\n- 打开网页、导航\n- 点击、输入等交互操作\n- 截图、录屏\n- 获取页面元素信息\n\n常用命令：\n```bash\nagent-browser open <url>        # 打开网页\nagent-browser snapshot -i       # 查看可交互元素\nagent-browser click @e1         # 点击元素\nagent-browser screenshot        # 截图\n```\n\n刚才帮你打开谷歌浏览器就是用的这个技能！需要我帮你做什么操作吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":178,"cacheRead":34215,"cacheWrite":605,"totalTokens":35004,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000049840000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000505}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774014703226}}
