{"type":"message","id":"bc6facea","parentId":"50165dbe","timestamp":"2026-03-20T13:54:50.134Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让我帮他打开谷歌浏览器，但之前他说要使用\"系统的打开浏览器功能\"，而不是 agent-browser 技能。\n\n在 Linux 系统上，打开系统默认浏览器通常可以使用 `xdg-open` 命令。让我尝试用这个命令来打开谷歌浏览器或者系统默认浏览器。\n\n我可以：\n1. 使用 `xdg-open https://www.google.com` 打开默认浏览器\n2. 或者尝试直接启动 google-chrome\n\n让我尝试用 xdg-open 打开 Google 页面，这样会使用系统默认的浏览器。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好的，小王子！让我用系统命令打开谷歌浏览器：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_15eecf27303b4f41a2d12cce","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"xdg-open https://www.google.com"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":23148,"output":163,"cacheRead":13477,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36788,"cost":{"input":0.00254628,"output":0.000045640000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00259192}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774014882347}}
